'''Thunder Alley''' was a region of space along [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] borders that several fleets rotated to patrol. In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]] just before the [[Black Fleet Crisis]], the [[New Republic Second Fleet|Second Fleet]] had been patrolling Thunder Alley the longest of the fleets without home service and shipyard services. [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Gial Ackbar]] convinced [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] to pull the Second Fleet out and replace it with the [[New Republic First Fleet|First Fleet]], which had been serving as [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] defense force during the same time.

